contentrichtext.text: '''Elea''' may refer to: * Elea, ancient name of an Italian{{spaced ndash}}Greek colony, now known as [[Velia]] **[[Eleatics]], school of pre-Socratic philosophers at Elea * Elea, ancient city in Greece in the regional unit of [[Thesprotia]] * a settlement of Cyprus in [[Kyrenia District]], see [[Elia, Kyrenia]] * a settlement of Cyprus in [[Nicosia District]], see [[Elia, Nicosia]] * [[Olivetti Elea]], a mainframe computer manufactured from 1959 through 1964 * [[Elea (bryozoan)]], an extinct genus of [[Cyclostomata|cyclostome]] [[Bryozoan]] ==See also== *[[Velia (disambiguation)]] {{geodis}}
